headline: Will Universal Health Services (UHS) Beat Estimates Again in Its Next Earnings Report?
summary: Universal Health Services (UHS) has an impressive earnings surprise history and currently possesses the right combination of the two key ingredients for a likely beat in its next quarterly report.

headline: UnitedHealth Q4 Earnings Beat on Strong Optum Rx, Offers 2026 Outlook
summary: UNH tops Q4 EPS estimates as Optum Rx drove growth, but profits plunged year over year, and management set a cautious 2026 outlook amid rising costs.
